<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>Mizuki Blue Amber Hotel</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/informations.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/header.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/footer.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/reservation_modal.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/reservation_modal_medias.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/calendar.css">
		<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="imgs/general/red_flower.png"/>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Quicksand" rel="stylesheet">
    	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Questrial" rel="stylesheet">
    	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto" rel="stylesheet">
    	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Cormorant+Upright" rel="stylesheet">
    	<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<%include partials/header.ejs%>
		<div class="main-content-container">
			<div id="informations-titles-container">
				<h1>Our hotel specific details</h1>
				<p>Here you can find specific and direct informations about all our hotel characteristics. In case you still have some doubts you can send us an email.</p>
			</div>
			<div id="informations-content-container">
				<div id="information-content-direct-container" class="options-mode">
					<%var infos_contents_titles_h2 = ["Rooms", "Check-in & Check-out", "Events", "Prices & Costs", "Structure", "Localization"]%>
					<%var infos_contents_texts_p = ["our Rooms", "our Check-in & Check-out processes", "Events", "the Prices & Costs", "our Structure", "our Localization"]%>
					<%for(var i = 0; i < 6; i++){%>
						<div class="information-content-div flip-card" content_index = "<%=i+1%>">
							<div class="flip-card-inner">
								<div class="flip-card-front">
									<div class="information-content-image-container">
										<img src="/imgs/informations/check_in.png">
									</div>
									<div class="information-content-title-container">
										<h2><%=infos_contents_titles_h2[i]%></h2>
									</div>
									<div class="information-content-text-container">
										<p>Click here to understand and know more about <%=infos_contents_texts_p[i]%>.</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div id="flip-card-back-checkin" class="flip-card-back">
									<div class="flip-card-back-title-container">
										<h2>Click to see all details about <%=infos_contents_texts_p[i]%></h2>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<p class="option-selected-click-to-go-back">Click again to go back to options</p>
						</div>
					<%}%>
				</div>
				<div id="content-selected-details-container">
					<h1>Informations about rooms</h1>
					<div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 100%;">
						<div id="content-selected-details-border"></div>
					</div>
					<div id="content-selected-details-texts-container">
						<p>We have four different types of rooms:</p>
						<p>The <span style="font-weight: bold;">"Common"</span> room, which is the cheapest, but still quite comfortable. The prices can vary from 95¥ to 117¥.</p>
						<p>The <span style="font-weight: bold;">"Standard"</span> room, which is the medium price and a very good option if you're looking for a very good room without spending too much. Prices go from 194¥ to 245¥.</p>
						<p>The <span style="font-weight: bold;">"Prime"</span> room, which is a very comfortable room with a little bit more expensive price, but of course, worth of it. Prices from 349¥ to 425¥.</p>
						<p>The <span style="font-weight: bold;">"Exclusive"</span> room. This room is best for you if you are looking for something really differentiated and as the name suggests, exclusive. Prices vary from 598¥ to 720¥.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div id="content-selected-details-container-mob">
				<h1>Informations about rooms</h1>
				<div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 100%;">
					<div id="content-selected-details-border-mob"></div>
				</div>
				<div id="content-selected-details-texts-container-mob">
					<p>We have four different types of rooms:</p>
					<p>The "Common" room, which is the cheapest, but still quite comfortable. The prices can vary from 95¥ to 117¥.</p>
					<p>The "Standard" room, which is the medium price and a very good option if you're looking for a very good room without spending too much. Prices go from 194¥ to 245¥.</p>
					<p>The "Prime" room, which is a very comfortable room with a little bit more expensive price, but of course, worth of it. Prices from 349¥ to 425¥.</p>
					<p>The "Exclusive" room. This room is best for you if you are looking for something really differentiated and as the name suggests, exclusive. Prices vary from 598¥ to 720¥.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<%include partials/footer%>
			<%include partials/reservation_modal%>
		</div>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/reservation_modal.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/informations.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/calendar.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="js/header.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>
